  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Abandoned 429 tear gas during Polduwa protest",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that the people who behaved restlessly at the Parliament entrance towards the Polduwa roundabout on the night of the 23rd, stole 429 tear gas and tear gas bombs from the police.",
        "Police sources say that 340 of them were tear gas bullets and 89 were tear gas bombs.",
        "Welikada police found 50 bullets and 340 tear gas bullets stolen by the protestors hidden in a house on Gotami Road, Borella.",
        "Police teams have started investigations to find the missing bullets and tear gas bombs."
      ],
